{"tid":366225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）保險男幫親戚整冷氣，切割器飛出變「刀削鼻」","createTime":"2017-08-19T23:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T06:13:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd92610192762fbc12dce7a8afc8b27de0de6e8","tid":366225,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T23:09:09.000Z","msg":"35歲的小彭在保險公司上班，從小都會親自修理家中大小事情，上周三中午小彭接到姨媽電話&hellip;&hellip;新居的裝修師傅忘記打開冷氣缺口<br />\n<br />\n當日&hellip;&hellip;小彭發現要打開安裝中央冷氣的維修缺口，需要先在衣櫃上方先開一個洞。<br />\n<br />\n他爬上梯子，戴上護目罩，拿起手提式電動切割器就開始工程。<br />\n<br />\n其間，小彭感覺切割器出現異常，說時遲那時快，切割器上拋光盤突然擦着他的臉飛出去，頭上眼罩和眼鏡都被震碎，半個鼻被割下來。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n他拿着半個被割下來的鼻到醫院救醫&hellip;&hellip;手術&hellip;&hellip;縫上鼻子。<br />\n<br />\n醫生檢示過他的鼻子後，表示他的鼻子有指壓反應，色澤還挺紅潤，故認為手術挺成功，應該不影響以後生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/070905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F070905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b6c87055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7999c9eb2262f63e2f4ce1c0b7da0576380a80ff","tid":366225,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強國"},{"pid":"0bf98baae9b02154167dae0ee580f938f76f7735","tid":366225,"uid":119695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"講還講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf776f63a7242bb6b77f582e9241c43a8ae9f69","tid":366225,"uid":44025,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/niusnews-imgs/354972_254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fniusnews-imgs%2F354972_254.jpg&h=d83f281c&s={SI